The Telegraph - Calcutta (Kolkata) | Bengal | DA hiked 8%
                                                                                                                     4                                                                                      DA hiked 8%
                            
	Calcutta, Nov. 9: The state government today announced the release of one instalment of dearness allowance, equivalent to 8 per cent of revised basic pay, for its employees with effect from December this year. Nearly 10 lakh employees, including teachers, will benefit.                                                                                                                                                                              
